Enum Server.Map

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Server.Map>
    Enclosing class:
    Server

    public static enum Server.Map
extends java.lang.Enum<Server.Map>
    The Map enum contains all Maps for the current Server Map can be accessed by name (Map.CentralPlain) or id (1002). Maps should be instantiated only once and therefore the Enum singleton pattern is used. Each Map contains a Collection of Entities, and has a constructor for Locations that are in this Map.
    Author:
    Jan-Willem Gmelig Meyling, Thomas Gmelig Meyling
